sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/GitOps
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Webhook as Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>mTLS
    participant DSCCtrl as DSC Controller<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    participant ComponentCtrl as Component Controller<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    participant Deployer as Manifest Deployer<br/>Kustomize Engine
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>9091/TCP HTTP

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 1: DataScienceCluster Reconciliation

    User->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply -f dsc.yaml<br/>Auth: kubeconfig credentials
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-datasciencecluster<br/>mTLS (API server cert)
    Webhook->>Webhook: Validate DSC spec
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: 200 OK (validation response)
    K8sAPI-->>User: DataScienceCluster created

    Note over DSCCtrl: Watch triggered on DSC creation

    DSCCtrl->>K8sAPI: GET /apis/datasciencecluster.opendatahub.io/v1<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>DSCCtrl: DSC resource

    DSCCtrl->>DSCCtrl: Reconcile DSC<br/>Determine desired state

    DSCCtrl->>K8sAPI: CREATE Component CRs<br/>(Dashboard, KServe, Workbenches, etc.)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>DSCCtrl: Component CRs created

    DSCCtrl->>K8sAPI: UPDATE DSC status<br/>Status: Progressing<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>DSCCtrl: Status updated

    Note over ComponentCtrl: Watch triggered on Component CR creation

    ComponentCtrl->>K8sAPI: GET /apis/components.opendatahub.io/v1alpha1<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>ComponentCtrl: Component CR (e.g., Dashboard)

    ComponentCtrl->>Deployer: Load manifests from /opt/manifests<br/>Filesystem read

    Deployer->>Deployer: Run kustomize build<br/>In-memory processing

    Deployer->>K8sAPI: APPLY manifests<br/>(Deployments, Services, ConfigMaps, etc.)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Deployer: Resources created

    ComponentCtrl->>K8sAPI: UPDATE Component status<br/>Status: Ready<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>ComponentCtrl: Status updated

    DSCCtrl->>K8sAPI: UPDATE DSC status<br/>Status: Ready<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>DSCCtrl: Status updated

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 2: Metrics Collection

    Prometheus->>DSCCtrl: GET /metrics<br/>via 8443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (ServiceAccount)<br/>TLS: service-ca
    DSCCtrl-->>Prometheus: Prometheus metrics

    Prometheus->>ComponentCtrl: GET /metrics<br/>via ServiceMonitor<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    ComponentCtrl-->>Prometheus: Component metrics

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 3: Component Deployment Monitoring

    User->>K8sAPI: kubectl get dsc -o yaml<br/>Auth: kubeconfig
    K8sAPI-->>User: DSC with status conditions

    User->>Prometheus: Access Prometheus UI<br/>via Route: HTTPS/443<br/>Auth: OpenShift OAuth Proxy
    Prometheus-->>User: Metrics dashboard
